desc_long							评测						“Starlaxis Supernova Edition is a delightful little find in a sea of crud at the cheaper end of the Steam store. It was a legitimately new gameplay experience that draws on mechanics that seem familiar but actually offer something quite different from what they initially appear.”Pixel Populi													Supernova-Edition!									Some of you may noticed that Starlaxis has been released on some other platforms too. However, on Steam you'll get the "Supernova-Edition" which includes improved graphics, more missions, better gameplay mechanic, a new commander and, of course, Steam Achievements, Trading Cards and Leaderboard!																						关于这款游戏							Prepare yourself for mind-blowing puzzle action in new dimensions!You think Starlaxis is just a small, easy puzzle game? THINK AGAIN!Master breath-taking challenges, win seemingly impossible boss fights, complete multiple missions goals, overcome dozens of enemies, and last but not least: Save  EARTH!FeaturesExplosive puzzle action with complex game mechanicsStory & Endless mode 5 huge worlds, each with 8-9 missions and different goals to accomplish Great graphic design with beatiful backgrounds and 3D spaceships Choose from 4 upgradable starships 6 commanders with their own signature “special moves” Seemingly impossible boss fights, breath-taking challenges, black holes, dozens of enemies, animated cutscenes and much more will entertain you for many hours STEAM FEATURES: Achievements, Trading Cards and LeaderboardNo DLC. Get the COMPLETE game when buying itJoypad, mouse & keyboard SupportPC-EXCLUSIVE						
